lyTime":"2021-04-17T09:43:23.000Z","msg":"我4 5歲已經開始有 如果訓晏覺夜晚訓覺就會出現 本身有焦慮症 試過食過一隻adhd藥增加多巴胺結果嚴重咗 後尾醫生開隻antipsychotic藥減多巴胺 而家少咗好多"},{"pid":"1ed3fa116915e4b7c4c51c4dd2039ccbdd5e1baa","tid":2492651,"uid":370482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09d577deefb992519cfd4f2da1203e73a18b170","tid":2492651,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37e41c128a5d102b5c4e38f238f62f633fde651","tid":2492651,"uid":370482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"上年第一次試過鬼壓床之後 就一直發作到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道自己醒咗但又郁唔到都幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"試吓輕力咬一下條脷，試過幾次都會即刻醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"淨係郁到少少手指尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次幾驚 仲以為見到耶穌 後尾就習慣咗 依家鬼都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5d5bb98f228af62b95363099c69609e5c5529f","tid":2492651,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:45:37.000Z","msg":"打得丁多"},{"pid":"b108f4302d5682099ccf88bef51f83107d6d8d5a","tid":2492651,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed3fa116915e4b7c4c51c4dd2039ccbdd5e1baa","tid":2492651,"uid":370482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b09d577deefb992519cfd4f2da1203e73a18b170","tid":2492651,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f37e41c128a5d102b5c4e38f238f62f633fde651","tid":2492651,"uid":370482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"上年第一次試過鬼壓床之後 就一直發作到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知道自己醒咗但又郁唔到都幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"試吓輕力咬一下條脷，試過幾次都會即刻醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"淨係郁到少少手指尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一次幾驚 仲以為見到耶穌 後尾就習慣咗 依家鬼都唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/appear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"👉當出現睡眠癱瘓應該怎麼辦👈<br />\n首先，我們要認識到睡眠癱瘓症是正常的現象，一般情況下並不會對身體健康造成不利影響。但當出現睡眠癱瘓的次數過於頻繁，嚴重影響休息質量時，應及時尋求醫學幫助。<br />\n在發生「鬼壓床」時，要先調整好自己的心態，告訴自己「這是正常的」，保持放鬆、平穩的呼吸，然後集中意念嘗試一些動作，嘗試逐漸恢復正常，如：首先快速轉動眼球，讓眼球上下左右做圓周運動，<span class=\"red\">一段時間後改為眨眼動作；然後收縮嘴巴周圍的肌肉，嘗試移動自己的舌頭（伸舌頭、咬舌頭）和下巴</span>。當你感覺身體開始可以慢慢移動時，嘗試移動脖子、肩部、手腳等，逐步恢復肌張力，最後再坐起來慢慢運動一下全身的肌肉。"},{"pid":"26f8d28bbdd206f61efa8b2637661c65e660fa1b","tid":2492651,"uid":178199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"我自己experience係, 太夜訓就位鬼壓床<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生物學講好似係身體太攰早過個大腦訓著左<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果發生我會好用力咁打開隻眼--&gt;醒左之後要令自己全醒(睇1分鍾手機/用手拍下塊臉)--&gt;再訓就唔會鬼壓床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}